body like that is--

00:23:04.780 --> 00:23:07.490
CHARLIZE THERON:
Especially that body.

00:23:07.490 --> 00:23:09.040
There's a lot to explore there.

00:23:13.850 --> 00:23:15.940
I've been very lucky.

00:23:15.940 --> 00:23:23.105
Jason is really, really
good at casting, obviously.

00:23:26.010 --> 00:23:29.070
No, but seriously, he's
