00:23:34.910 --> 00:23:36.890
And I didn't know who
Patton Oswalt was,

00:23:36.890 --> 00:23:39.440
so I was a little bit
like, ooh, who's this?

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:42.080
And then he showed me some
stuff, and I was like, really?

00:23:42.080 --> 00:23:46.250
And then we got on set, and
it was like, oh, god, that's--

00:23:46.250 --> 00:23:48.392
you just see something.

